            <title>到手价低至 4999.2 元火影推出 2025 款焕 16 Air 笔记本：R7 H 255 + 16G + 1T + RTX5060（原价 6599 元）</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/875/745.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/875/745.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Fri, 15 Aug 2025 13:41:57 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
